name.k: LiveTunes - ライブコンサート・シミュレータ

platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 好きな曲があっという間にエキサイティングなライブコンサートに

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The next time we have friends over or need extra pep in our workout playlists, we’re launching this nifty music player. Cue up a song, choose a venue, and LiveTunes amps up the reverb and crowd noise to match. Outdoor Festival is especially heart-thumping and Coffeehouse sounds beautifully stripped down. Plus, swiping up for the on-demand applause never, ever gets old.
